# Cloudflare Pages — SPA routing for the two entries.
#
# /admin/* → serve the admin SPA's index.html (admin handles its own
#            hash routing internally for #pr / #vs / #shop / etc.)
# /*       → serve the public SPA's index.html (router in main.js
#            maps the path to a tab — /news, /pr, /vssound, /shop,
#            /tools, /about, /news/{id} for individual articles)
#
# Order matters: Cloudflare evaluates top→bottom and stops at the
# first match. /admin must be listed before /* so admin URLs don't
# fall through to the public SPA.

/admin/*  /admin/index.html  200
/*        /index.html        200
